query: Retrieve the addresses and submission dates of buildings where house sharing is prohibited.
sql: SELECT Address, Recorded Date FROM House_Share_Prohibited_Buildings_List;

query: Find the addresses and latitudes of buildings where house sharing is prohibited, recorded on November 3, 2021.
sql: SELECT Address, Latitude FROM House_Share_Prohibited_Buildings_List WHERE Recorded Date = '11/03/2021';

query: List all violation types and total fines for vacant and abandoned buildings.
sql: SELECT Violation Type, Total Fines FROM Vacant_and_Abandoned_Buildings_-_Violations;

query: Find the violation types and latitudes of vacant and abandoned buildings with violations issued on March 7, 2011.
sql: SELECT Violation Type, Latitude FROM Vacant_and_Abandoned_Buildings_-_Violations WHERE Issued Date = '03/07/2011';

query: Retrieve the names and addresses of all Chicago public schools.
sql: SELECT Name of School, Street Address FROM Chicago_Public_Schools_-_Progress_Report_Cards__2011-2012;

query: Find the names and phone numbers of Chicago public schools located in the ZIP code 60623.
sql: SELECT Name of School, Phone Number FROM Chicago_Public_Schools_-_Progress_Report_Cards__2011-2012 WHERE ZIP Code = '60623';

query: Retrieve the names and addresses of all libraries.

query: Find the names and phone numbers of libraries located in the ZIP code 60643.
